Photo Gallery | 2014-15

REDSHIRT JUNIOR (2014-15)

Appeared in 21 games and made one start…averaged 2.2 points and 1.5 rebounds per game…scored a season-high eight points in a 72-50 victory over Cal State Dominguez Hills (12/18).

PRIOR TO CAL STATE FULLERTON

Played the 2013-14 season at Arizona Western College in Yuma, Ariz…averaged 10.4 points per game shooting 44.4 percent from the floor…added 32 three-pointers and 5.4 rebounds per game…spent the 2012-13 season at College of the Canyons in Santa Clarita, Calif…redshirted the 2011-12 campaign at New Mexico State.

HIGH SCHOOL

A 2011 graduate of El Camino Real High School in Woodland Hills, Calif…played four years on the varsity squad for head coach David Rebibo…averaged 14.3 points, 9.0 rebounds and 1.5 blocks per game as a senior.
